  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick skillet or wok over medium heat.",
    "Brush the lotus leaves with sesame oil and set aside.",
    "In the skillet, combine ginger, garlic, and garam masala. Cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the tofu and cook until lightly browned.",
    "Stir in soy sauce, honey, salt, and pepper. Cook for 1 minute.",
    "Warm the lotus leaves in the skillet for 30 seconds on each side.",
    "Spoon the rice into the center of each leaf, leaving a 1-inch border.",
    "Add the tofu mixture on top of the rice.",
    "Fold the leaves in a triangle and cook for 2 minutes on each side.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
